# Run build after changes

After any edit, change, or **undo** (reverted edits) in this project (templates, content, static files, or build script), run the site build:

```bash
python build.py
```

Run this from the project root (`c:\git\insinistra-site`). The build outputs to `dist/`.

Do not skip this step after changes or undos unless the user explicitly asks to skip it.
